            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2 group-hover:text-pink-600 transition">Revenue Optimization</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Maximize your store's revenue potential with data-driven strategies</p>
            </div>
